/*
 * Tokenomics
 * Name - LuckyFarm
 * Symbol - LFC
 * Supply - 1 billion
 * 10% transaction tax decreasing over time
 * 3% directed to LFC/WBNB liquidity pool
 * 4% (sent as BNB) to Lucky Farm marketing wallet
 * 3% (sent as BNB) to Luck Farm owner wallet for LFC buybacks and burn
 */

